{"tid":2020796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地政總署將視察南豐紗廠口罩工場 如有違規則先發警告信要求糾正 強調是次行動不涉及刑事檢控","createTime":"2020-05-17T10:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:50:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e0cf00cf25e244533a3d3b337eba9bddab8ae5","tid":2020796,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"地政總署將視察南豐紗廠口罩工場了解有否違規<br />\n17.05.2020 18:14<br />\n<br />\n荃灣南豐紗廠借出空間讓政府生產「銅芯抗疫口罩」。有傳媒報道，口罩工場所在的「第五廠」地段已活化，地契不容許工業用途，質疑有違規情況。地政總署證實口罩工場所在的地段，可作用途不包括工業或倉庫，總署表示會安排分區地政處職員，進行實地視察及了解情況，並作出跟進，但強調總署只以地主身份執行地契條款，行動不涉及刑事檢控。<br />\n<br />\n根據契約條款，地政總署如發現建築物違反契約條件，一般會發警告信要求業主糾正；最嚴重可收回有關地段或把相關權益轉歸政府。行政長官林鄭月娥月初曾經到過南豐紗廠的口罩工場視察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288075&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288075%26csid%3D261_341&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e610aSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=df3b8b6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288075&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9a36ceae9ac4987f0f7feef327253efc20bcb1fa","tid":2020796,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"咁幾時拉鳩柒婆"},{"pid":"f402a2f90d746ccccad5bd18b307e8e71f687d83","tid":2020796,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156657053105f22628b10af6388a4cea5d8c909a","tid":2020796,"uid":35696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢地政署長一定有豁免權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297c474f498be6925760fe28805ce3376fb5a4e1","tid":2020796,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"香港人可以為左湄公河而爆seed，咁今日可唔可以為左自己而爆seed?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2020376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2020376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65506ac43ec5912b6c69ffc28b9bd2a6263bbde9","tid":2020796,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"156657053105f22628b10af6388a4cea5d8c909a","tid":2020796,"uid":35696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢地政署長一定有豁免權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"係對自己人有豁免權"},{"pid":"1a8af775feecc14f99d76e3ffd7de6a40763b308","tid":2020796,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"156657053105f22628b10af6388a4cea5d8c909a","tid":2020796,"uid":35696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢地政署長一定有豁免權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"用唔緊要，基本上而家已經係玩無恥，乜都鑑操黎，今次目的如果是落柒婆面其實都算達成<br />\n<br />\n由佢派得人落去睇，甚至俾傳媒第一次問個時無交代過已事前已seek署長approval ，就證明做野掛一漏萬，唔跟程序....只可以不停咁後兜/解釋，甚至要大話冚大話"},{"pid":"cbeb5cc54bbf16fc8b6721cc5182d7546767188c","tid":2020796,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:24:32.000Z","msg":"地署：沒足夠證據南豐紗廠違地契<br />\n地政總署回覆查詢稱，荃灣葵青地政處於上月18日視察南豐作坊後，發現有房間放置10多部縫紉機，上址業主表示，作坊曾借出部分空間予香港紡織及成衣研發中心作研發新口罩，以及訓練縫紉工人和紙樣製作工人；徵詢法律意見後，認為無足夠證據證明該地方的使用違反相關土地文書條款。地政處上月25日再派員視察，所有縫紉機亦已移除。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200607/s00002/1591468094065/%e5%9c%b0%e7%bd%b2-%e6%b2%92%e8%b6%b3%e5%a4%a0%e8%ad%89%e6%93%9a%e5%8d%97%e8%b1%90%e7%b4%97%e5%bb%a0%e9%81%95%e5%9c%b0%e5%a5%91\" data-sr-ur